General.Name: Ellen AB (publ)
General.Description: Ellen AB (publ) provides pH-balanced intimate health products for women. It offers ellen Probiotic Tampon; ellen pH-Control, a medical device, which is used to measure the vaginal pH at home; ellen Aqua Block Tampon, which is designed to prevent water from entering the vagina during bathing and swimming; and ellen Probiotic cream, a moisturizing and pH-balancing intimate cream that prevents irritation. The company also provides ellen Probiotic Cleansing Foam to clean intimate areas, as well as used as a shaving cream; ellen Prebiotic Deo Spray, an intimate deodorant; and ellen Prebiotic After Shave & Wax Gel that soothes the sensitive intimate area after shaving or waxing. It sells its products through distributors and retailers; and through online. Ellen AB (publ) was incorporated in 1991 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
